Class PacketDataOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • com.whirvis.jraknet.stream.PacketDataOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.DataOutput, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class PacketDataOutput
extends java.io.OutputStream
implements java.io.DataOutput
    Used to write data to a Packet with ease, to retrieve a Packet's DataOutput simply use getDataOutput().
    Author:
    Whirvis T. Wheatley
